ISLAMABAD, April 09 (APP):The ECP has imposed a ban on officer transfers in NA 148 Multan district until the conclusion of by-elections and announcement of the winning candidate on May 19.
According to the spokesperson, the ECP has also announced a ban on government functionaries or elected representatives, including local government for announcing any development scheme for NA 148, Multan district, until the declaration of by election’s results.
